Stream movies online

Need help deciding what to watch before your popcorn runs out? We’ve got you covered! With this guide, you can find the best movies to watch online across all languages, eras, and genres—all in one place. From discovering where to watch films for free to keeping track of new releases, our easy-to-use guide is your go-to hub for all things movies.

Where to Watch Movies Online?

Want to know where to stream your favourite films online? Our movie streaming guide helps you track where to buy, rent, or stream films across all major platforms. Our user-friendly search filters make it easy to find films based on your personal preferences. For example, if you're interested in revisiting the golden era of Bollywood, simply click on the ‘Release Year’ filter and adjust it to select the era you’d like to explore.

Looking for recommendations tailored to your interests? With JustWatch, you can filter results by genre and browse streaming options for romance, action, thrillers, musicals, comedy, and many more. Just click on ‘Genre,’ select the ones that appeal to you, and start browsing the best films based on your preferences.

You can also filter films by IMDb ratings, age ratings, price, streaming availability, video resolution, and more.

Watch Movies for Free

In addition to helping you find where to stream films online, our movie streaming guide also provides pricing details for each title. There are plenty of free films available that don’t require a subscription or any additional charges. Simply click on ‘Free’ under our pricing filter to browse a rich collection of films you can watch at no cost.

You can also make the most of your subscriptions by exploring our dedicated guide pages to see what’s available on streaming services such as Netflix, Hotstar, Zee5, JioCinema, Amazon Prime Video, and other major platforms.

Find the Best Movies to Stream

From larger-than-life South Indian action blockbusters like RRR and Baahubali to feel-good Disney-Pixar favourites like Finding Nemo and Toy Story, JustWatch’s movie library offers a diverse selection of films spanning various genres, languages, and time periods.

Our streaming guide includes all-time classics such as acclaimed Bengali filmmaker Satyajit Ray’s directorial debut, Pather Panchali, the timeless It’s a Wonderful Life, and Kabhi Khushi Kabhie Gham, a quintessential 2000s Bollywood film packed with emotion.

Expand your search beyond films by exploring our movie and TV streaming guide to discover everything new and trending on your favourite streaming platforms. You can also visit our TV streaming guide to focus specifically on TV shows and web series.


Stay up to date with all the upcoming films arriving on streaming services with the help of our guide.
